main event: A UFO was visually observed at an elevation of 20,000+ feet from an aircraft on June 8, 1963.
interesting points: The object was observed for a total of 10 minutes,The sighting was documented as part of Project Blue Book,The UFO was reported to be headed on a course of 330 degrees true,The report concluded with insufficient data for evaluation, and no specific identification of the object was made.
witness description: The sighting was reported from an aircraft but no witnesses are specifically confirmed.
